    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It is still in wonderful shape and has been really well-loved! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it runs smoothly and looks fantastic both inside and out. It\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
