      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional linear power delivery through its factory individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system was recently overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains composed with a refreshed suspension setup including Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes for sharpened turn-in. While the finish shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the drivetrain is peak-performing and the limited-slip differential locks predictably. A mechanically sorted, driver-focused example ready for the circuit or the backroads.",
